.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, water
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, kale, peas
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, tulip, dahlia, bellflower
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, alhambra, blend, chaman
 1. the person who growsdahlia is between the ritmeester-smoker and the person who growstulip##2
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the alhambra-smoker##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the chaman-smoker##8
 5. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the left of the person who growstulip##8
 6. the person eating peas is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the left of the chaman-smoker##5
 8. the blend-smoker is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who growszinnia is the alhambra-smoker##1
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
11. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the left of the person who growsdahlia##8
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
14. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person who growstulip##8
18. the person eating grapes is not to the right of the alhambra-smoker##8
19. the person drinking water is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | sprite | water  | milk  |
| Food          | peas     | grapes | carrot | kale  |
| Flower   | tulip    | dahlia  | bellflower | zinnia |
| Cigar           | blend | chaman | ritmeester    | alhambra  |

