.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, skydiving, sudoku
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, yellow, blood-red, emerald
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, electronic, folk, jazz
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, car, ship, skateboard
 1. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person who likes emerald##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
 5. the person driving the ship is not to the right of the person who likes brown##8
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person who likes blood-red##8
 7. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
 9. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
10. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes brown is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
12. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | sudoku   | skydiving | card-games |
| Color   | brown     | blood-red  | emerald   | yellow      |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | blues    | folk      | jazz       |
| Transport         | ship    | train | skateboard   | car    |

