.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, cucumber, plum
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bongani, blend, bolivar
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, lizard, hamster, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, golf, rowing, tennis
 1. the blend-smoker is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
 2. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 3. the person eating plum is the owner of the hamster##1
 4. the person eating banana is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the lizard##2
 5. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person eating banana##8
 7. the bolivar-smoker is in an odd position##4
 8. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##5
 9. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
10. the owner of the lizard is the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
12. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
13. the blend-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
14. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
15. the tiparillo-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Food    | cucumber    | banana             | apple   | plum     |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | blend            | bolivar | bongani    |
| Pet     | lizard | mouse | hedgehog  | hamster |
| Sport   | basketball  | golf               | rowing  | tennis   |

