.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, trike, train, skateboard
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, pilot, software-developer, doctor
There are 4 different nationalities: british, malaysian, polish, russian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, handball, skiing, volleyball
 1. the fisherman is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
 2. the russian is the person driving the trike##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is not the person driving the airplane##6
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the software-developer##1
 5. the fisherman is not to the right of the polish##8
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the fisherman##8
 7. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
 8. the malaysian is the pilot##1
 9. the british is not to the left of the person driving the skateboard##8
10. the software-developer is not to the left of the fisherman##8
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person driving the skateboard and the pilot##2
12. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
13. the malaysian is not to the right of the pilot##8
14. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the pilot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Transport         | skateboard     | airplane | train   | trike  |
| Job   | doctor | fisherman   | pilot     | software-developer  |
| Nationality   | british    | polish     | malaysian | russian  |
| Sport         | skiing     | volleyball | cricket   | handball |

