The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, december, october, august
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the left of the pilot##8
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
 4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is the dunhill-smoker##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the havana-smoker##8
 7. the person drinking sprite is not the swisher-smoker##6
 8. the manager is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the person drinking sprite##7
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the manager##5
10. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the manager##3
11. the musician is on the right of the freelancer##1
12. the manager is not the cain-smoker##6
13. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
15. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the right of the manager##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
