.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, tea, water
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, june, february, march
4 different games are played: go, mah-jongg, canasta, backgammon
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bus, taxi, trike
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 2. the person driving the airplane is not the person who's birthday is in september##6
 3. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
 4. the person playing canasta is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
 6. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking milk##7
 7. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
 8. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in june##7
 9. the person playing go is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##8
11. the person playing go is on the far left##1
12. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the trike is the person who's birthday is in february##1
14. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
15. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
16. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | milk        | iced-tea      | water      | tea          |
| Birthday       | march | february     | september | june       |
| Game         | go | canasta | mah-jongg  | backgammon |
| Transport   | taxi        | trike         | bus        | airplane     |

