 9. the person watching documentary movies is not to the left of the person who likes brown##8
10. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
11. the person traveling to london is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
12. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
