.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, mirinda, water
4 different pets are kept: goat, frog, mouse, hedgehog
House: futuristic, townhouse, victorian, modern
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, quad-bike, snowmobile
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the modern house##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the townhouse house##8
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the victorian house##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
11. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
13. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the townhouse house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee   | water     | mirinda    | iced-tea |
| Pet   | goat  | hedgehog      | mouse     | frog     |
| House         | futuristic | victorian  | modern     | townhouse  |
| Transport     | bike     | quad-bike | snowmobile | boat     |

