.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, soy-milk, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, magic-tricks, skydiving
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, bolivar, havana, prince
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, epic, crime, musical
 1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 2. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
 3. the person drinking sprite is the bolivar-smoker##1
 4. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the prince-smoker##5
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the dannemann-smoker##8
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 8. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
 9. the person watching epic movies is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
10. the havana-smoker is not the person watching time-travel movies##6
11. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
12. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the prince-smoker is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
14. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | cola      | sprite  | soy-milk | juice        |
| Hobby         | skydiving | chess   | baking   | magic-tricks |
| Cigar   | prince    | bolivar   | havana    | dannemann      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic   | musical | crime   | time-travel    |

