The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter, subway, van
 1. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 2. the person traveling to new-york is not to the right of the electrician##8
 3. the person traveling to berlin is the pakistani##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 5. the pakistani is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to nizza##5
 6. the person driving the van is the german##1
 7. the police-officer is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
 8. the musician is on the far right##1
 9. the electrician is not to the right of the indonesian##8
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to new-york##5
12. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##5
13. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the police-officer##8

.:: Answer ::.
