.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, august, october, january
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, polish, canadian, indonesian
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, fisherman, photographer, project-manager
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, roller, subway
 1. the canadian is not the person who's birthday is in october##6
 2. the dancer is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
 3. the indonesian is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 4. the dancer is not to the left of the polish##8
 5. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
 6. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the left of the photographer##8
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the thai##3
10. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the project-manager##7
11. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
| Birthday    | october        | august        | june        | january   |
| Nationality       | polish      | thai      | indonesian | canadian |
| Job         | project-manager | photographer | fisherman     | dancer  |
| Transport   | roller          | jet-ski      | quad-bike     | subway  |

