.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, singing, sudoku
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, social-worker, teacher
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, peas, lemon, tomato
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, prince, siglo, ritmeester
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the bartender##8
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 3. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the right of the siglo-smoker##5
 4. the teacher is the person eating tomato##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is not the social-worker##6
 6. the person eating zucchini is not to the right of the prince-smoker##8
 7. the person eating peas is not to the left of the social-worker##8
 8. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 9. the siglo-smoker is in an even position##4
10. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
11. the person eating zucchini is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is singing is between the social-worker and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku    | singing   | board-games   | collecting |
| Job           | bartender | doctor    | social-worker | teacher    |
| Food   | lemon   | zucchini | peas     | tomato    |
| Cigar   | pall-mall   | siglo      | prince         | ritmeester     |

 